data.description: Adorable Mini farm with 15.466 acres of fenced-in land and a 2 bedroom 1 bath home. The property includes a small farm house, barn, corn crib, storage shed, and a 500 square foot garden bed. This property is perfect for anyone interested in homesteading or small-scale farming or just looking to get some ideally located land. Conveniently located less than 10 minutes from Danville with highly rated schools. Must see to appreciate the beauty of the land and surrounding woods. The home is sold as-is but inspections welcome. Survey and appraisal available upon request! Schedule your showing today!
